fig.label: Figure 1

caption.p: Vaccine effectiveness against influenza A(H3N2) viruses overall and by age and genetic subgroup, Canadian Sentinel Practitioner Surveillance Network, 2018/19 (n = 1,993)

fig.p: CI: confidence interval; NE: not estimated; VE: vaccine effectiveness.

Adjusted VE estimates with 95% CI are displayed. All VE estimates are adjusted for age group, province, specimen collection interval and calendar time. Methods are detailed in Supplement S2 and model specifications and VE estimates with precise CI are provided in Supplementary Table S9.
